## 轻量化网络笔记

#### 1. Why Architecture Matters?

- Representation Power

different architecture have different representation power, such as linear network have its limit to represent difficult patterns

- Optimization Characteristic

Optimization for deep network have many difficults, resnet and densenet proposal different structure for a better optimizing performance.

- Generalization

a general model have its power to do different work

- Efficiency

In mobile or edge situation, and so on.

#### 2. Advances in Neural Architecture Design

- Stage I: Using fancy architecture to achieve high performance in contest.
- Stage II: going mature, using simple rules to design network
- Stage III: aimed at diverse purpose.

#### 4. Dynamic Neural Networks

- ##### Bigger is better

big model have more parameters to solve corner case, so it’s better.

- ##### Why do we use the same expensive model for all images?

using small and cheap models for easy images; using big and expensive models for hard one.
